1. Introduction
Welcome to Classified Ads. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application, Classified Ads. Please read this policy carefully to understand our views and practices regarding your personal data and how we will treat it. By using our app, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

2. Information We Collect
Personal Information
We may collect the following personal information:

Name, contact details (phone number, email address) when you register or post ads.
Location information to help users find ads based on geographical relevance.
Non-Personal Information
We may also collect non-personal information, which cannot identify you, such as:

Device information (model, operating system version, and unique device identifiers).
Browsing information within the app, such as categories viewed and searches made.
3. How We Use Your Information
We use the information collected for the following purposes:

To Provide Services: Deliver, maintain, and improve our app’s functionality.
To Personalize User Experience: Display relevant ads based on your preferences and location.
To Communicate with You: Send notifications related to your ads or account activity.
To Ensure Security: Monitor and analyse usage for fraud prevention, and address violations of our terms.
4. Sharing Your Information
Third-Party Service Providers
We may share your information with third-party service providers that assist us in app functionality, analytics, and advertising.

Legal Obligations
We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities (e.g., a court or government agency).

Business Transfers
If we are involved in a merger, acquisition, or asset sale, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction.

5. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no internet or electronic transmission is entirely secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.

6. Your Privacy Choices and Rights
Access and Update
You can access and update your information directly within the app. If you need assistance, please contact us at ubuyint@gmail.com.

Delete Your Account
You may delete your account at any time. Once deleted, your personal information will be removed from our active databases but may remain in archived copies for legal compliance.

7. Children’s Privacy
Our app is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you become aware that a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the app and updated on this page with the "Effective Date" above. Your continued use of the app following any amendments signifies your acceptance of the changes.

9. Contact Us
